title: Re: Keen Oggs
content:
Hmm, not bad, but you didn't maximise the volume before you encoded the files - so they sound really quiet compared to 'real' music.

What program did you use to play the IMFs? It doesn't sound like Adplug or anything, the percussion sounds a bit 'harsher.'

Oh, and you didn't put any tags in the files [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-cheeky.gif[/img] Any particular reason why you prefer them in Ogg as opposed to IMF, though?
